ueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011428, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O that One who is (Ever existing) Supreme Being and was there before any and everything, then (after that) He created all things. He is eternal and all that has been created is mortal. O that One like unto Him there is nothing. O that One who is such that no one in the high heavens, nor in the low earths, nor above, below and in between, worship anyone other than Him as a God. Praise to be Thee. It is not possible to count up, remember and narrate Thy praise in all its dimensions. Thou alone can do it. Therefore send blessings on Muhammad and on the children of Muhammad, blessings that no one other than Thou has the capacity to count, remember and narrate its meaning and true purpose.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay woh jo har cheez se pehle maujood tha, phir har ek cheez ko paiyda kiya. Tu woh hai jo baaqi rahega aur har cheez fanah ho jaayegi, ay woh jiske maanind koi cheez nahi, ay woh jo na buland aasmaano mein hai aur na pistareen zameeno mein, aur na unke upar aur na unke neeche hai aur na darmiyaan mein hai. Woh Ma’bood jiske siwa koi ma’bood nahi Tere liye hamd o sana hai, woh hamd keh koi usey shumaar (count) nahi kar sakta siwaaye Tere, pas Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma, woh rehmat keh koi usey shumaar (count) nahi kar sakta siwaaye Tere.", "Urdu": "اے وہ جو ہر چیز سے پہلے موجود تھا پھر ہر ایک چیز کو پیدا کیا تو وہ جو باقی رہے گا اور ہر چیز فنا ہو جائے گی اے وہ جس کے مانند کوئی چیز نہیں اے وہ جو نہ بلند آسمانوں میں ہے اور نہ پست ترین زمینوں میں ہے اور نہ ان کے اوپر اور نہ ان کے نیچے ہے اور نہ درمیان میں ہے وہ معبود جس کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں تیرے لئے حمد ہے وہ حمد کہ کوئی اسے شمار نہ کر سکے سوائے تیرے پس حضرت محمدؐ و آل محمدؐ پر رحمت نازل فرما وہ رحمت کہ کوئی اسے شمار نہ کر سکے سوائے تیرے۔", "RArabic": "YAA ZAL LAZEE KAANA QABLA KULLE SHAI-IN SUMMA KHALA-QA KULLA SHAI-IN SUMMA YABQAA WA YAZNAA KULLO SHAI-IN YAA ZAL LAZEE LAIY-SA KAMIS-LE-HI SHAI-OON WA YAA ZAL LAZEE LAIY-SA FIS-SAMAA-WAA-TIL O’LAA WA LAA FIL ARZEE-NAS SUFLAA WA LAA FAWQA-HUNNA WA LAA TAHTA-HUNNA WA LAA BAIYNA-HUNNA ELAA-HUN YOA’BADO GHAIRO-HU LA-KAL HAMDO HAMDAN LAA YAQWAA A’LAA EH-SAAA-E-HI ILLAA ANTA FA-SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN SALAA-TAN LAA YAQWAA A’LAA EH-SAAA-E-HAA ILLAA ANTA.", "ArabicText1": "یَاذَاالَّذِیْ کَانَ قَبْلَ کُلِّ شَیْٓءٍ ثُمَّ خَلَقَ کُلَّ شَیْٓءٍ ثُمَّ یَبْقٰی وَیَضْنٰی کُلُّ شَیْٓءٍ یَاذَا الَّذِیْ لَیْسَ کَمِثْلِہٖ شَیْٓءٌ وَیَا ذَا الَّذِیْ لَیْسَ فِی السَّمٰوَاتِ الْعُلٰی وَلَا فِی الْاَرَضِیْنَ السُّفْلٰی وَلَا فَوْقَھُنَّ وَلَا تَحْتَھُنَّ وَلَا بَیْنَھُنَّ اِلٰہٌ یُعْبَدُ غَیْرُہٗ لَکَ الْحَمْدُ حَمْدًا لَا یَقْوٰی عَلٰی اِحْصَآئِہٖ اِلَّا اَنْتَ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ صَلٰوۃً لٰا یَقْوٰی عَلٰی اِحْصَآئِھَا اِلَّا اَنْتَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicTex